Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}零即是無
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能想到這一點的印度人真是太厲害了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比起這個 我更想知道高中備考的對策
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.77,0:02:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼國二的園子在教姐姐念書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糰子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木其實比許多家教還聰明呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然看不太出來就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我也想請教功課的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好呀 你的成績挺讓人擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}事情太多 整個夏天我都沒好好念書
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}升上國三前的成績都還不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以前好極了 但現在卻爛透了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:51.99,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}House！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:03:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒辦法嘛 升上國三發生了太多事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也多虧風風學姐的努力 才有現在的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.76,0:03:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是想入勇者社的乃木園子耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是那個乃木園子？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是兩年前大橋事件中的勇者耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請大家多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼傳說中的勇者會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為待在家裡也沒事好做？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就這種理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我小學輟學了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}居然把這麼沉重的事輕輕帶過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}解除了使命的乃木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}向大赦申請回歸正常的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真沒想到能回歸正常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊 沒想到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}傳說中的前輩真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歡迎偉大的前任勇者 乃木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}叫我乃木或者園子就行了 風風學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}風…？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請多指教 小魚乾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰告訴她的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樹就叫寸寸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}寸寸？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈就叫悠悠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好棒 那我就叫你小園吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就說好了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它叫桑喬 請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是個奇妙的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來大家是這樣度過青春的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小園
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歡迎來到勇者社
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我之後也要享受青春啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}躺在床上時我就一直看著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想著勇者社這麼有趣 一定很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:05:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒想到又能上學了 真開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就開始念書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從我喜歡的複數矩陣開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:12.15,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}複數矩陣就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完全不懂 聽不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你夏凜 星期天還麻煩你來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼 今天剛好很閒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 不過你今天真的超帥的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也不賴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者社真是奇怪的社團
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以才開心啊 每天都有不一樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太陽下山了 又要明天再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又要禮拜一了嗎 假期過得真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回去還得寫作業呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我已經寫完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}白天不是一直在比賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那還用問 禮拜六就寫了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凜真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蛋糕？怎麼帶進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天有家政課
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有這招啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是小樹做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:06:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}做太多 我就帶過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的妹妹真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是獨特的品味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請說是表現力豐富
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先不論外表
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐很專業啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小樹做的東西終於能吃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐 這麼說有點傷人喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}寸寸 寸寸 開蛋糕店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以後還要辦加盟店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}園子想像力太豐富了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我都不知道是不是裝傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不管多少都吃得下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還是夏凜吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不不 應該給小樹吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我上課已經吃過了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}園子別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}社長才是 別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是吃兩個 女子力就不保了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還不都是風 你幹嘛切成六塊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道 習慣成自然嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}習慣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 只是…下意識的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}五等分完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼切出來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}經過數學計算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}牡丹餅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以前在社辦吃過牡丹餅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前友奈在家政課上做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甜食時間結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來做星期天的練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.75,0:09:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三 我終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好久不見 過得還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不對 不該這麼問的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的是好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}INES的醬油豆冰淇淋和那家店一起消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好可惜 時間總是不等人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三 我加入勇者社了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是讚州國中的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她們都好有趣 絕對不輸給我們的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天週六 我要和她們一起去幼稚園演戲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也會演好一棵樹的 一定要看喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對了 這是我在家做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回想三三怎麼炒的 自己還原了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是三三的 如果好吃要稱讚我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是我的份 然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼我會做三份呢 三三
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木還沒來嗎 快要開始了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}訊息還沒變成已讀 是還在睡覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}準備的時候 園子還那麼興奮的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然只是演棵樹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒辦法 今天就不要樹了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你怎麼也怪怪的 要上場囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身體不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我身體沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我總覺得有種說不出來的奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天要不要中止活動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者社的大家 謝謝你們今天過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其實我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}孩子們很期待今天的戲劇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.25,0:12:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每天都很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}演吧 他們都等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就是窮凶惡極的魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要來抓幼稚園裡不聽老師話的孩子們啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一起大鬧一番吧 不用忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下魔王 不許你教壞孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}居然在我面前狂妄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者不管受了多重的傷也沒有放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是所有人都放棄 世界就會落入黑暗的魔爪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一個又一個人倒在了魔王腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知不覺只剩下勇者一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有人知道勇者是孤獨的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪怕孤獨 勇者也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:14:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要不放棄 就永遠都還有希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}無論失去了什麼 我都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我都不想失去最寶貴的朋友們！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:15:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…明明答應她要…永遠在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有園子 你們到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們現在的記憶是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}發生了某種非常不妙的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然不清楚是什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我們卻以為那件事沒發生過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.28,0:15:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者社裡 還有一位我們寶貴的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我怎麼可能忘記 絕對不可以忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼我會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈 冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家快想起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡有過一位叫東鄉美森的社員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.61,0:16:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對喔 話說東鄉現在去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉美森
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是乃木家的園子唷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有嚇到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們從今天起就是同班同學了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:16:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}園園…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}heyhey～鷲鷲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是園子唷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}園園…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嚇到了嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}驚喜作戰大成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:13.11,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}園園！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別…別這樣啦～鷲鷲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是想入勇者社的乃木園子耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木園子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.07,0:17:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是兩年前大橋事件中的勇者耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.87,0:17:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請大家多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒想到還能和園園一起上學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是我上課打瞌睡 記得叫醒我唷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.21,0:17:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你得自己注意才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺東鄉就像媽媽一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}命運之輪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喔～感覺好帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}宿命中的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我原來是命運之子呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Fortune！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:17:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}福德圓滿！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有無法避開的重大變故的意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你怎麼了 表情那麼怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}國防假面…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在流傳在大街小巷的謎之英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有這樣的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人們呼喚我守衛國家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人們吶喊我守住愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}憂國戰士 國防假面參上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.89,0:18:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人們呼喚我守衛國家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人們吶喊我守住愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}憂國戰士 國防假面參上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}逮捕！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼會！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是國防假面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.64,0:18:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當人們受到邪惡勢力的威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會儘可能現身的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}儘可能…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}找到你了 東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}該從什麼問起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}國防假面來我們社了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上次真的很謝謝你在危急時幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:23.06,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請您和我握個手 握手 握手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}發生過什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有次晚上友奈把錢包弄丟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}國防假面幫她一起找錢包了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺國防假面好親切 為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是當然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天為什麼會光臨勇者社呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這…這是…因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}國防假面就是我啊 友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們已經知道囉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎…怎麼會！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.78,0:19:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}國防假面竟然就是東鄉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不是在演吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.26,0:19:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你說對不起大家 又是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.56,0:20:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身體恢復之後 我總是坐立不安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.23,0:20:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我曾經破壞了牆壁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖說只是一時衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但也給世界帶來了重大的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是不可原諒的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一直想著自己該如何償還過失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以…就想做些什麼來贖罪…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.11,0:20:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以當起了國防假面…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鷲鷲現在好極端呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然能理解你的心情 但太過頭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}國防假面超帥的 我也好想當啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.62,0:20:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其實別看我這樣 我可是國防假面二號呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我就來當三號！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.82,0:20:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別再增加了啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是夏凜也模仿起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跑出個魚乾假面該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我才不會去學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.71,0:21:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們都有一份為大家努力的心的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是呀 鷲鷲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有什麼事都可以來依靠一下我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈 園園
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼我們…都沒有關於東鄉的記憶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就好像她從一開始就不存在於世上一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.69,0:21:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.31,0:21:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我明明是社長 卻又…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:22:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但已經都想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.31,0:22:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼 到底發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鷲鷲…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.40,0:22:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你現在在哪裡…在做什麼呀…
Comment: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:35.59,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}言葉にならないキミの声を聞いた気がした
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.86,0:22:41.27,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}どんな秘密　胸に抱えているの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.27,0:22:46.72,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}水辺に影ひとつ　浮かべた思い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:52.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}あの日なにも　声を掛けられなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:58.76,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}細い背中　消えそうだった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.76,0:23:04.33,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}ああ　今走り出せば（動き出した刻）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:09.83,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}キミに追いつくかな（揺るぎない瞳）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.83,0:23:14.60,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}未来に結いつけた（その糸も）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:20.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}決してその糸を離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.56,0:23:25.75,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}花降る　寂寞の中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:31.27,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}花散る　まだその前に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.44,0:23:36.32,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}キミは独りなんかじゃないよと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.32,0:23:42.50,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}この光を届けに行くだから…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:46.49,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}最後のひとひら　繋ぎ止めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.49,0:23:54.19,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}もう少しだけ Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:35.59,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}我彷彿聽到了 無法描述的你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.86,0:22:41.27,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}心中 究竟懷著怎樣的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.27,0:22:46.72,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}岸邊形單影隻的我 突然回憶起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.84,0:22:52.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}那一天 自己沒有叫住你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:58.76,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}你纖弱的背影 卻要消失在我的眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.76,0:23:04.33,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}要是現在奔跑起來（行動之時）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:09.83,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}能追上你的足跡嗎（耿直的視線）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.83,0:23:14.60,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}連接今天與明天的（一根紅線）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:20.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}求你不要放開
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.56,0:23:25.75,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}花落 是你的孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:31.27,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}花散 請等等我的腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.44,0:23:36.32,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}我想說 你不是孤單的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.32,0:23:42.50,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}我這就把光芒帶到你的身邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:46.49,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}最後的花瓣 求你不要飄零
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.49,0:23:54.19,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}再給我一點時間 Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.35,0:24:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.88,0:24:03.37,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一鼓作氣上啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.99,0:24:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這真的很不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.58,0:24:05.51,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好酷的船呀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.59,0:24:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要平安回來啊 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.51,0:24:06.45,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.53,0:24:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}無論多少次 我都會救你的！
